description:
Presenting an exceptional opportunity to secure a quality parcel of Land in one of Melbourne’s quickest growing suburbs.

This excellent block offers a 12.5-meter frontage and 32-meter depth and is the perfect foundation for building your family’s dream home or gaining the benefits of owning an investment property in a continually evolving location.

Situated within a hop, skip and a jump to all major amenities including the recently upgraded Rockbank Train Station, Western Freeway access and future Town Centre with grocery stores, spots clubs, schools, health services and a short drive to Melbourne CBD, there is no better time to purchase in a thriving community!

Please contact us for more information.
